# Displays

set $display1 DP-6
set $display2 DP-5
set $display3 DP-4
set $display4 eDP-1 

output $display4 position 1920 1080 resolution 1920 1080
output $display2 position 1920 0 resolution 1920 1080
output $display1 position 0 0 resolution 1920 1080
output $display3 position 3840 0

#output $display3 scale 1.5

